<div class="twofa_popup" id="twofa_popup">
<div class="twofa_popup-wrapper">
<div class="twofa_popup-title">
Enable Two-Factor Authentication
</div>
<div class="twofa_popup-text">
<p>To access the admin area, you will need to setup two-factor authentication (TFA).</p>
</div>
<div class="twofa_popup-setupbtn twofa_popup-btn" id="twofa_popup-setupbtn">Setup now</div>
</div>
